Show what mode is it now on server name(support any Language) with txt file

-command-
"l4d_current_mode", "", "League notice displayed on server name"

-example-
modify configs\hostname\server_hostname.txt: [中文亞洲] Asia L4D 惡靈勢力中文房名
write command: l4d_current_mode "Harry's mod"

The Server name will be "[中文亞洲] Asia L4D 惡靈勢力中文房名 (Harry's mod)"
